sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser / React Page
    participant Store as Redux Store
    participant Query as RTK Query API Layer
    participant API as Backend API
    participant State as marketdata.Store

    Browser->>Store: read settings, filters, refresh interval
    Browser->>Query: subscribe to endpoint query
    Query->>API: OPTIONS preflight when needed
    API-->>Query: CORS headers
    Query->>API: GET /api/v1/* + X-API-Key
    API->>State: Snapshot or focused latest-state read
    State-->>API: latest data
    API-->>Query: JSON response
    Query->>Store: cache data and request status
    Store-->>Browser: render cards, tables, stale/error state
